  "title": "Sales Executive (HORECA)",
  "description": "<p><u>Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>Identify and source for new accounts and new business opportunities</li><li>Canvass for new customer (include cold calls)</li><li>Build and maintain good working relationships with potential and existing clients</li><li>Set and achieve sales targets individually and as a team</li><li>Handle all customer enquiries </li><li>Regular visits to customer to understand their requirements</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><u>Requirements</u></p><ul><li>Minimum 2-3 years' sales experience in HORECA</li><li>Aggressive & sales driven</li><li>Able to work independently </li><li>5 days week</li><li>Singaporean & PR preferred</li></ul><p><br /><u>Salary Package</u><br /> - Salary  + Car allowance + Commission package more than $36,000 to $70,000 per annum.<br /> - High Sales Commission <br /> - Transport & Mobile Reimbursement</p>",
